                    <span>It takes a lot of time to work thru the examples in this book. (I use Excel to speed things up). But it's a great book. First read it at around 1970. Still in love with it.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Remembered for years</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
